title: Córdoba
page_copy: Listen to radio stations from Córdoba, from a wide variety of genres like News, Pop, Spanish, Sports and Talk.  Enjoy stations such as Magic80, Radio Marca, Europa FM, Hit FM Córdoba, Canal Sur Radio and more.  Come find the top new songs, playlists, and music!  Listen on your iPhone, iPad, iPod Touch, Android, Blackberry, and other app-enabled mobile phones.
